item.description:
The Boston Healthcare IT Professionals meetup is under new management, and we would like to have an informal initial meetup to get to know each other and generate ideas for future events. We’ll be meeting at the Thelonious Monkfish restaurant in Central Square in Cambridge (this is a change from the original venue - Mary Chung).

In order to generate ideas, please come with one or two topics that interest you or that you would be interested in learning more information about. We will have some time to do introductions, as well.
